      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000151",
    "sentence": "膠東、菑川、濟南王皆伏誅。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000152",
    "sentence": "酈將軍攻趙，十月而下之，趙王自殺。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "將軍",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 1,
        "end": 3
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000153",
    "sentence": "濟北王以劫故，不誅。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000154",
    "sentence": "初，吳王首反，并將楚兵，連齊、趙。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000155",
    "sentence": "正月起，三月皆破滅。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000156",
    "sentence": "贊",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000157",
    "sentence": "贊曰：荊王王也，由漢初定，天下未集，故雖疏屬，以策為王，鎮江淮之間。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "漢",
        "label": "ORG",
        "start": 9,
        "end": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000158",
    "sentence": "劉澤發於田生，權激呂氏，然卒南面稱孤者三世。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000159",
    "sentence": "事發相重，豈不危哉！",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000160",
    "sentence": "吳王擅山海之利，能薄斂以使其眾，逆亂之萌，自其子興。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000161",
    "sentence": "古者諸侯不過百里，山海不以封，蓋防此矣。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000162",
    "sentence": "朝錯為國遠慮，禍反及身。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_035_000163",
    "sentence": "「毋為權首，將受其咎」，豈謂錯哉！",
    "entities": []
  }
